    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es waddu us to Zeltu\ntahs Taifnibas/ widdu starp tahs\nTeefas Tekkahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka es manneem Mihto-\ntajeem leeke eemantecht weenu\npastahwigu Buhfchanu/ un es\npilditchu winno Mantu Kam-\nbarns.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS turreja\nmanni tai * Gefahkumâ fawa\nZelta muhscbam/ preeksch faveem\nDarbeem/ pirms tee Laiki ktua.\n* Eebr: Wall: ir tà : To Gefahkumu fawo\nZetto, ka Kristus nofaukts tohp Par: Jahn: 3,\n14. tas irr, kas wihs Leetas ar Deewu to\nTehwu un fwehtu Garlu raddijs : Kol: 1, 16.\nEbr. 1, 2.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es efinu no Muhscibas\nfwaidita/ no Gefahkuma pirms\nta Semme tappe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es dsimmu/ kad tee Dsit-\nkumi wehl ne bija/ kad tee Awo-\nti ar Uhdeni wehl ne tezzeja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pirms tee Kalui tappe\ndibbinati/ preeksch teem Pakal-\nneim/ etmu es dsimmusi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch wehl ne bij to\nSemmi darrijs/ neds tohs Lau-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad wiꞥſch tahs Debbe-\nfis fatatsija/ tad es btju/ kad\nwiꞥſch tohs Dsittumus ar E-\nschahin apdarrinaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad wiꞥſch tahs Padeb-\nbesis no augshenes stipri nolikfe/\nkad wiꞥſch stiprinaja tohs Awo-\ntus to Dsittumu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad wiꞥſch Juhrai fawu\nRohbeschu zehle/ ka tas Uhdens\nwinna Paiwehletchann ne pahr-\nkahptu. Kad wiꞥſch tahs Sem-\nmes Dibbitus likfe/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad biju es fahnis wiꞥ-\nnu tas Istaisitajs/ un biju ik-\ndeenas (winna) Gelihgsmoſcha-\nna/ un jakteju preeksch winna\nwiﬀa Laika.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es jaktejohs winna Pa-\nfaules Wirfû/ un manna Lihgf-\nmiva irr pee teem Zilweka Behr-\nneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad klausajt mann nu/\nmanui Behrni/ jo swehtigs irr\ntas/ kas mannis Zettus targa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Klautajt to Pamahzischa-\nnu/ un tohpeet gudri/ un ne at-\nmetteet winnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Swehtigs irr tas Zil-\nweks/kas mannis klausa/ kas ik-\ndeenas pee mannahin Durivini\nnomohda irr/ un gaida pee man-\nnu Durwju Stendereem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo kas mann atrohd/ tas\natrohd to Dsihwibu/ un dabbuhs\nPatikschann no ta KUNGA.\n"
    },
